contiguous to the other primitive Rocks.-<lb/>
- Primary Marble is known from<lb/>
other Marbles, by the distinct<lb/>
crystallizations of its texture which<lb/>
            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
