- It is a general fact, of considerable<lb/>
importance - That where a Coast is<lb/>
Mountainous &amp; elevated, a correspondent<lb/>
depth of Sea occurs close to the Land.<lb/>
|_&amp; in many cases this circumstance<lb/>
produces very extensive &amp; beneficial<lb/>
