&amp; it is owing, <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">as I stated on Saturday</del>
            <lb/>
to this depth of water, near the Shores,<lb/>
that the Northern Sea for 12 degrees<lb/>
of Latitude is preserved open, &amp; free<lb/>
from ice, in the coldest Winter. -<lb/>
