the sea is soon closed by the first<lb/>
severe Cold. -<lb/>
Were the high North seas frozen<lb/>
our Winters would be infinitely more<lb/>
severe than they are at present,<lb/>
&amp; our summers, much more wet<lb/>
&amp; disagreeable. |_And there is<lb/>
